            <h2><a class="title" href="/ramadan-mubarak/" rel="bookmark">Ramadan Mubarak!</a></h2>
            <div class="info">
              <span class="date">July 20th, 2012</span> <span class="comments"><a href="/ramadan-mubarak/#comments">9 comments</a></span>
              <div class="fixed"></div>
