            <div class="content">
              <p style="text-align: center;"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ramadan-Quilt-Wall-hanging.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-2456" title="Ramadan Quilt Wall hanging" src="/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Ramadan-Quilt-Wall-hanging.jpg" alt="" width="402" height="568"  sizes="(max-width: 402px) 100vw, 402px" /></a></p>
              <p>The holy month has arrived, a time for compassion and reflection &#8230; as well as&nbsp;family,&nbsp;food &amp; faith.</p>
              <p>Wishing you a generous and blessed Ramadan.</p>
